channel.title: [PI] Cache On cachedownloader got weird error[Pi]
channel.description:
oke so i made a webclient from the scratch,
so now my normal client + webclient have the same problem
when the cache is downloaded is unpacking well... then i log in, i can see the chat box saying welcome to nightmareX ur rank is 3 atm
but the playing screen stays black with "loading please wait" on it
on the webclient and client it does that, so i thougt hmm weird maybe i made a mistake by zipping the cache
so i looked in program files and cant find my fucking cache.... its just not there i was sure and double checkedcd it i called it nightmareX_cache i even tryed it on my laptop
so any one got a idea?
